# Amplify Hosting's Next.js SSR runtime expects a flat node_modules layout.
# pnpm's default symlink linker breaks Amplify's "find node_modules/next at
# the artifact root" check — hoisted produces an npm-style flat install.
# Required per https://github.com/aws-amplify/amplify-hosting/blob/main/FAQ.md
node-linker=hoisted
